OL,3,CCharities and councils warn of
OL,4,Cchildren's social care 'breaking point'
OL,6,FThe latest Government figures show
OL,7,Fthere were 621,880 referrals to
OL,8,Fchildren's social care in the year to
OL,9,FMarch 31, 2024 ` equivalent to 1,704 a
OL,10,Fday.
OL,12,FNearly 400,000 children were
OL,13,Fclassified as being in need of support
OL,14,Fand protection in the same period,
OL,15,Fwhile 50,000 were on child protection
OL,16,Fplans due to the severity of risk.
