OL,3,CCharities and councils warn of
OL,4,Cchildren's social care 'breaking point'
OL,6,FThe Local Government Association (LGA)
OL,7,Fsaid 224,520 investigations were
OL,8,Fcarried out last year to establish if
OL,9,Fa child was suffering, or at risk of,
OL,10,Fsignificant harm.
OL,12,FMore than half of children involved
OL,13,Fwere found to have abuse or neglect as
OL,14,Ftheir primary need, with factors such
OL,15,Fas domestic abuse and mental health
OL,16,Fplaying a significant role.
