OL,3,CCharities and councils warn of
OL,4,Cchildren's social care 'breaking point'
OL,6,FThe Government has stated its
OL,7,Fintention to address these issues with
OL,8,Fmeasures in the Children's Wellbeing
OL,9,Fand Schools Bill, supported by a
OL,10,Fchildren's social care prevention
OL,11,Fgrant. Several funding streams have
OL,12,Falso been consolidated into a new
OL,13,Fchildren and families grant.
OL,15,FBut providers of support to children
OL,16,Fsaid these measures are not currently
OL,17,Fsufficient to meet the scale of the
OL,18,Fchallenge.
