OL,3,CCharities and councils warn of
OL,4,Cchildren's social care 'breaking point'
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the the Children's
OL,7,FCharities Coalition, which includes
OL,8,FAction for Children, Barnardo's, The
OL,9,FChildren's Society, National
OL,10,FChildren's Bureau and the NSPCC, said:
OL,11,F"All children have the right to grow
OL,12,Fup in safe and happy homes.
OL,14,F"Yet through our services and networks
OL,15,Fwe are hearing directly about a
OL,16,Fchildren's social care system at
OL,17,Fbreaking-point, desperate for
OL,18,Finvestment in order to respond with
OL,19,Fthe right support at the right time
OL,20,Fwhen children are at risk or in need.
