OL,3,CCharities and councils warn of
OL,4,Cchildren's social care 'breaking point'
OL,6,F"Frontline workers carry out vital
OL,7,Fwork supporting vulnerable children
OL,8,Fand families in progressively
OL,9,Fchallenging circumstances.
OL,11,F"However, with chronic underfunding
OL,12,Fand councils trapped in a downward
OL,13,Ffinancial spiral unable to meet
OL,14,Fdemand, we should not be waiting for
OL,15,Fchildren to be in harm's way before
OL,16,Fthey receive help and we should be
OL,17,Fgiving families the support they
OL,18,Fdeserve."
