OL,6,FA recent study led by academics at
OL,7,FUniversity College London found one in
OL,8,Ffour children in England need social
OL,9,Fcare services by the time they turn
OL,10,F18, amid warnings over poverty and
OL,11,Fspending cuts.
OL,13,FThe study has led to questions about
OL,14,Fwhether the current focus on snapshot
OL,15,Fannual children social care figures
OL,16,Fprovides a complete picture to
OL,17,Fofficials and decision-makers.
