OL,6,FArooj Shah, chair of the Local
OL,7,FGovernment Association's children and
OL,8,Fyoung people board, described support
OL,9,Ffor children and young people as
OL,10,F"central to the delivery of the
OL,11,FGovernment's mission to break down
OL,12,Fbarriers to opportunity".
OL,14,FShe added: "With investment in
OL,15,Fchildren's social care and partner
OL,16,Fagencies including mental health
OL,17,Fprovision, we can focus on early
OL,18,Fintervention and preventing children
OL,19,Ffrom reaching crisis point, where the
OL,20,Flevel and costs of support are
OL,21,Fsignificantly higher.
