OL,6,F"The spending review is an opportunity
OL,7,Ffor long-term, sustainable funding for
OL,8,Fchildren's social care and the
OL,9,Fservices children and families rely
OL,10,Fon, that puts the sector on a stable
OL,11,Ffooting and provides the support that
OL,12,Fenables every child to thrive."
OL,14,FRachael Wardell, president of the
OL,15,FAssociation of Directors of Children's
OL,16,FServices, said safety and stability is
OL,17,F"not the reality for too many children
OL,18,Fin this country".
