OL,7,Fcontinue to face significant and
OL,8,Fgrowing challenges, and we need a
OL,9,Fchild-first approach to national
OL,10,Fpolicymaking.
OL,12,F"As these shocking figures suggest, we
OL,13,Fneed to shift both focus and funding
OL,14,Ftoward early help and prevention for
OL,15,Fchildren and families, rather than
OL,16,Fjust responding once they're already
OL,17,Fin crisis."
